headline.main: Abroad; Hitler Has Also Lost a Political Battle in Moscow

lead_paragraph: A fateful question has been answered in Moscow, and the sense of the answer has already spread through Europe. While the official report will not be published until today, the effects of the conference are as visible in Germany, in the Balkans, in all the continental nations, as were the first repercussions of the collapse of Italy.
abstract: A O McCormick on Yugoslav campaign into Hungary and significance of Balkan fighting
